  "texts": [
    "In their work, three interaction-focused models based on the BERT Large model were introduced: BERT Last-Int, BERT Mult-Int, and BERT Term-Trans.",
    "Last-Int extracts features from the last layer of the [CLS] embedding and then combines them with a weight parameter.",
    "Inspired by BERT Last-Int, BERT Mult-Int extracts features from the [CLS] embeddings of all layers.",
    "Each layer's [CLS] embedding is first combined with a weight parameter, and the features of all layers are then integrated.",
    "Term-Trans produces a transition matrix for the query and the document, and then integrates the transition matrices from all layers via mean pooling."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}